2152
01:57:44,690 --> 01:57:46,692
FOX: I just have to stay calm.

2153
01:57:46,726 --> 01:57:48,895
If I start getting nervous, I'm
going to say the wrong thing.

2154
01:57:48,928 --> 01:57:51,564
I just have to stay calm.

2155
01:57:51,597 --> 01:57:54,567
FOX, VOICE-OVER: There's a protocol in
